          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#665e5d' fontsize='11'>Key Insights</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#665e5d' fontsize='10'>• The UK job market shows higher competition levels for Data Analyst roles.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#665e5d' fontsize='10'>• SQL and Excel remain the most consistently required skills 
in both markets.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#665e5d' fontsize='10'>• Many job postings do not clearly specify the required experience level.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#665e5d' fontsize='10'>• Tableau appears more frequently in UK job postings than 
in Polish listings.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
